Drupal View block's exposed filters don't work in node I have a view block with three exposed filters that work fine within the view, but not when called within a node. It worked fine when I first called it in the node, but has since stopped working. I've tried recreating the view block, recreating it in an entirely new view, and calling it from a new node. The exposed filters do absolutely nothing when clicked.

I have AJAX enabled (when disabled, the exposed filters disappear).

Any ideas why this isn't working?

